      "body" : "JsonParser().parse() is deprecated in newer versions of Gson. Use <code>JsonObject jsonObj = JsonParser.parseString(str).getAsJsonObject()</code>or  <code>Gson gson = new Gson(); JsonElement element = gson.fromJson (jsonStr, JsonElement.class); JsonObject jsonObj = element.getAsJsonObject();</code>"
